---
title: Curried Veggie Biryani with Sweet Potato, Peas, and Herbs
description: Biryani, an Indian mixed rice dish, can be composed of a variety of spices, herbs, and vegetables. Our version uses creamy sweet potato, sweet peas, and a fragrant mix of curry powder, garlic, and fresh mint for flavor.
